==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Underspore
<hw>Un`der*spore"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To raise with
a spar, or piece of wood, used as a lever.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Give me a staff that I may <qex>underspore</qex>.</q>
<rj><qau>Chaucer.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Understair</ent>⟦br⟧
